msgctxt "100_Upstart Yakuza"
msgid "I knew you were a lost cause! I'm talking about cold,\\r\n"
"hard cash here. I've got no use for you without it!"
msgstr "¡Sabía que no tenías remedio! Estoy hablando de \n"
"dinero en efectivo. ¡Sin, eso no me sirves de nada!"

msgctxt "112_Seasoned Yakuza"
msgid "Urgh..."
msgstr "Urgh..."

msgctxt "148_Saejima"
msgid "The hell do you think you're doin'? It don't take a genius to figure out you two're yakuza."
msgstr "¿Pero qué estás haciendo? Es obvio que ambos son yakuza."

msgctxt "160_Upstart Yakuza"
msgid "Keep moving, asshole! It's none of your damn business."
msgstr "¡Sigue tu camino, idiota! No es asunto tuyo."

msgctxt "172_Saejima"
msgid "It is now. Ya got dozens of eyes on you out here, and none of 'em wanna see you mess this guy up."
msgstr "Ahora lo es. Hay decenas de personas mirando y\n"
"nadie quiere ver, como le destrozas la cara a este tipo."

msgctxt "184_Seasoned Yakuza"
msgid "I appreciate what you're trying to do, sir... but stay out of this, please. It really has nothing to do with you."
msgstr "Agradezco su intención, señor... Pero, por favor.\n"
"No se meta, esto no tiene nada que ver con usted."

msgctxt "196_Seasoned Yakuza"
msgid "I deserve everything that's coming to me."
msgstr "Merezco cada golpe que me está dando."

msgctxt "208_Saejima"
msgid "(This guy can't be serious...)"
msgstr "(Este tipo no puede estar hablando en serio...)"

msgctxt "220_Seasoned Yakuza"
msgid "I'm sorry, Katagiri-san. I'll get the money as soon as I can, just please... have mercy on me, sir!"
msgstr "Lo siento, Katagiri-san. Conseguiré el dinero tan pronto\n"
"como pueda, pero por favor... ¡Tenga piedad, señor!"

msgctxt "244_Katagiri"
msgid "...Ugh. Way to go and take all the fun outta this."
msgstr "... Ugh. Qué manera de arruinar toda la diversión."

msgctxt "256_Katagiri"
msgid "Listen, Irie. You still owe us half a mil in tribute. If you don't pay up quick, you're gonna be paying with your pinkie. Got that?"
msgstr "Escucha, Irie. Todavía nos debes medio millón en tributos.\n"
"Si no pagas rápido, vas a hacerlo con tu meñique. ¿Entiendes?"

msgctxt "340_Saejima"
msgid "Irie-han, is it? What was that all about?"
msgstr "Irie-han, ¿Verdad? ¿Qué fue todo eso?"

msgctxt "352_Irie"
msgid "Who... are you?"
msgstr "¿Quién... Eres?"

msgctxt "364_Saejima"
msgid "Don't matter. Just an ex-yakuza lookin' out for one of his own."
msgstr "Eso no importa. Solo soy un ex-yakuza dándole la mano a un compañero."

msgctxt "376_Irie"
msgid "Huh. You must have been pretty famous if you don't want me knowing your name."
msgstr "Oh. Debes ser bastante famoso si no quieres que sepa tu nombre."

msgctxt "388_Saejima"
msgid "Look, just forget it, yeah? Now tell me, what was that punk beatin' up on ya for?"
msgstr "Mira, olvídalo, ¿Sí? Ahora dime, ¿Por qué te golpeaba ese idiota?"

msgctxt "400_Irie"
msgid "It's actually kind of embarrassing... You see, Katagiri-san and I belong to a family with an office down Tenkaichi Alley."
msgstr "Es algo vergonzoso... Katagiri-san y yo pertenecemos a una\n"
"familia por el Callejón Tenkaichi."

msgctxt "412_Irie"
msgid "I asked for more time to come up with my unpaid family tribute, but it seems to have rubbed him the wrong way."
msgstr "Le pedí más tiempo para pagar mi tributo a la familia,\n"
"pero como ves, se lo tomo muy mal."

msgctxt "424_Saejima"
msgid "Katagiri, huh? Clearly ya got a few years on him, not to mention boatloads more class. How'd a guy like that end up your boss?"
msgstr "Katagiri, ¿Eh? Claramente, tienes más años que él,\n"
"sin mencionar que eres mucho más educado.\n"
"¿Cómo terminó un tipo así siendo tu jefe?"

msgctxt "436_Irie"
msgid "I am older, yes, and have spent at least a decade longer in the family. But Katagiri-san is the patriarch's wonder boy."
msgstr "Sí, soy mayor que él y tengo al menos diez años más en la\n"
"familia. Pero Katagiri-san es el prodigio del patriarca."

msgctxt "448_Saejima"
msgid "Him? Ya don't say."
msgstr "¿Él? No me jodas."

msgctxt "460_Irie"
msgid "It's not surprising. Katagiri-san rakes in by far the most cash for the family."
msgstr "No es de extrañar. Katagiri-san es con diferencia\n"
"el que más dinero gana para la familia."

msgctxt "472_Saejima"
msgid "Tsk. It's like chasin' yen is all yakuza can think about nowadays."
msgstr "Pff. Parece que el dinero es lo único que le\n"
"importa a los yakuza hoy en día."

msgctxt "484_Irie"
msgid "Welcome to the 21st century, friend. Organized crime is nothing more than a chess game with money as the ultimate prize."
msgstr "Amigo mío, bienvenido al siglo XXI. Hoy en día el crimen\n"
"organizado no es más que un juego donde un saco de dinero\n"
"es el máximo premio."

msgctxt "496_Irie"
msgid "Old-school fist hurlers like me don't have a place in that intellectual stuff... More and more we're just weighing our families down."
msgstr "Los de la vieja escuela, como yo, no tenemos cabida contra los\n"
"intelectuales... Poco a poco, solo nos convertimos\n"
"en un agobio para nuestras familias."

msgctxt "508_Saejima"
msgid "I don't believe that for a second. Why don't ya just smack that sack around a bit? He'll change his tune."
msgstr "No te creo nada. ¿Por qué no le das una paliza? Cambiará su actitud."

msgctxt "520_Irie"
msgid "Not a chance."
msgstr "De ninguna manera."

msgctxt "532_Irie"
msgid "Katagiri-san has helped my family grow almost exponentially. And besides, he's my superior, regardless of how he got there. There's no fighting that."
msgstr "Katagiri-san ayudó a mi familia a crecer exponencialmente. Además,\n"
"es mí superior, independientemente de cómo llegó.\n"
"No voy a luchar con él."

msgctxt "544_Saejima"
msgid "Guess I can't argue with ya there. Sorry for buttin' into your family matters."
msgstr "Supongo que no puedo convencerte. Siento haberme entrometido, \n"
"en los asuntos de tu familia."

msgctxt "556_Irie"
msgid "It's all right. And really, I do appreciate the concern. Now if you'll excuse me, I need to go drum up some cash... quick!"
msgstr "No pasa nada. Realmente, aprecio tu preocupación. Ahora,\n"
"si me disculpas, tengo que ir a conseguir dinero... ¡Y rápido!"

msgctxt "580_Saejima"
msgid "(Money, money, money. This world's even colder than I remember.)"
msgstr "(Dinero, dinero, dinero. Este mundo es más frío de lo que recordaba.)"

msgctxt "592_Saejima"
msgid "(...Hm. Irie said his family's office is down Tenkaichi Alley, right? Might be worth payin' them a visit.)"
msgstr "(Mm... Irie dijo que la oficina de su familia está en el Callejón Tenkaichi, quizá sea buena idea hacerle una visita.)"

